## handoff
- produced: built + deployed demo at `public/demos/telehealthy/` (index.html + assets); registered in workSamples.js id:10; demo-src source at `upwork-runs/telehealthy/demo-src/`
- decisions: frontend-only, no Flask blueprint; scripted fallback is primary CI/Playwright path; WebLLM optional via "Load AI" button; recharts for analytics charts; 4-tab layout (Inbound hero, Outbound, CRM, Analytics)
- next needs: deploy step pushes `michaelwegter.com` to GitHub Pages (just the demo files + workSamples.js change); no mw-backend push needed; deploy-test exercises the scripted Inbound path (not WebGPU) via Playwright
- risks: recharts bundle is 604kB (173kB gzip) -- warrants noting but acceptable for a demo; WebLLM still lazy-loaded and will fail in headless -- scripted path covers all 3 intents fully for CI
